      <title>瑞银称瑞士资本规则将意味着更高的利润留存率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/ubs-says-swiss-capital-rule-would-mean-higher-profit-retention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团首席财务官托德·塔克纳 (Todd Tuckner) 表示，瑞银集团必须通过提高利润保留来满足瑞士政府的任何新资本要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/ubs-says-swiss-capital-rule-would-mean-higher-profit-retention</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 10:23:33 GMT</pubDate>
